
Step 1: User provides alcohol type

Step 2: We make an API call based on alcohol type

Step 3: FIRST API call returns  (1)DRINK NAME (2)DRINK IMAGE (3)DRINK ID
Based on data from the FIRST API call, we can show the user 5 drinks cards/ options


Step 4:
Place an event listener on each card.
If a card is clicked, pass in that cards “drinkID” to the SECOND api call to get 
(1) Ingredients
(2) Measurements
(3) Instructions
(4) We already have the cocktail name
(5) We already have the cocktail image
